description: Welcome to The Ceinture. This two-bedroom, two-bathroom Southwest-facing corner residence offers a blend of luxury and convenience in a prime location. Enjoy high-end finishes like custom kitchen cabinetry, Bosch stainless steel appliances, Arabesco Quartz countertops, built-in Sonos speakers, and oak-engineered hardwood flooring throughout. The in-unit washer/dryer adds convenience, while the primary bedroom offers a fully customized walk-in closet. Complete with a garage parking space with a storage locker. At the Ceinture, a professionally managed luxury condominium built in 2021, residents benefit from exceptional amenities, including a concierge, a fitness center, a club room with a catering kitchen, and a spacious 2,000+ square foot rooftop deck with outdoor seating and gas grilling stations. Perfectly situated steps from The Broadway Red Line T-stop and the best restaurants/shops in South Boston, this residence is on the border of both the South End and Seaport District!
